TwitterSearch is a component written in PHP making use of the Twitter's Search API.

It allows the user to enter an array of query terms and request a number of tweets back.

The component ships with it's own autloader and is fully unit tested.

Requirements:

PHP >= 5.3

Mockery - A PHP Mock object framework (required when running unit tests)

Zend_Http (included) - Used to make HTTP requests to Twitter

